These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Color: lilac, turquise, yellow, red
Food: carrot, garlic, pineapple, peas
1. Color:turquise is between Color:lilac and Food:garlic##2
2. Color:turquise is on the left or right of Food:carrot##3
3. Color:turquise is somewhere between Color:red and Color:lilac##7
4. Food:garlic is in an even position##4
5. Color:red is on the right of Food:pineapple##1
6. Food:garlic is somewhere to the left of Food:carrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Color   | yellow | red       | turquise | lilac        |
| Food      | pineapple  | garlic | peas        | carrot |

