2. Transport:boat is somewhere to the left of Transport:scooter##5
3. Transport:boat is somewhere to the right of Game:whist##5
4. Transport:van is on the left of Transport:boat##1
5. Game:whist is between Game:bridge and Game:billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Transport     | trike | van       | boat         | scooter     |
| Game   | billiard   | whist | bridge | monopoly |

